Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.32,0:02:15.32,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,That's all. Just for your information.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.32,0:02:17.82,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Wh-What are you talkin' about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.82,0:02:19.24,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Don't play dumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.99,0:02:21.78,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,This has gotten as hard as a rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.63,0:02:25.79,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,When you think about her, \Nyou get a lump in your throat,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.09,0:02:28.47,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,and you can't get the food down, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.56,0:02:31.62,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Poor thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.27,0:02:34.26,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,You're completely lovesick.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.26,0:02:37.07,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,L-Love?! This is love?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.07,0:02:40.46,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you've never fallen in love before?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.46,0:02:41.74,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.74,0:02:43.26,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,You've got to be kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.86,0:02:48.45,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Wait. If he really falls for that girl,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.45,0:02:52.99,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,then he won't get between Ri and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.37,0:02:58.86,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,All right, we'll skip jazz after school today and meet up to make a game plan instead.
