Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.53,0:03:02.20,sign,Sign,0,0,0,,{\c&H788BA8&\bord0\shad0\blur.75\fs40\fscy80\fnBell Gothic Std Light\frx4\fry8\frz5.676\pos(918,317)}Summer \NSale
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.49,0:03:04.38,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Huh? At my house?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.38,0:03:06.31,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,We ain't goin' to Ri'ko's basement?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.31,0:03:09.56,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,You'll be able to relax more at home, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.56,0:03:11.25,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,I don't mind, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.20,0:03:16.77,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,She might overhear us if we discuss our plans in the basement.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.74,0:03:18.76,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.56,0:03:21.67,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,This is Ri's shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.67,0:03:24.64,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,We live in a row house, so our places are connected.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.15,0:03:27.97,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Hey, Ma!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.97,0:03:29.18,apollon main,Kota,0,0,0,,Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.18,0:03:31.96,apollon main,Sachiko,0,0,0,,Welcome home, Bro! You're \Nback early today, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.96,0:03:33.30,apollon main,Kota,0,0,0,,Play with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.30,0:03:35.86,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Hold on, hold on. Where's Ma?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.86,0:03:38.57,apollon main,Sachiko,0,0,0,,Ma, Bro's home!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.23,0:03:38.04,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Richie!{alt}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.57,0:03:41.32,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,What're you doin'? Come on in.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.74,0:03:49.32,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Ma, this is Richie.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.32,0:03:51.04,apollon main,Ma,0,0,0,,Oh, hello there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.04,0:03:53.38,apollon main,Ma,0,0,0,,I appreciate you always looking out for Sentaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.07,0:03:56.43,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Oh, you're too kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.94,0:03:59.96,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Don't be shy. Dig in, Richie.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.77,0:04:05.46,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I thought you didn't have an appetite today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.46,0:04:06.92,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,I can {\i1}always{\i0}{\fscx120} {\fscx100}eat watermelon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.92,0:04:09.98,apollon main,Ma,0,0,0,,Sentaro loves his watermelon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.85,0:04:14.53,apollon main,Ma,0,0,0,,He told me he wasn't feeling hungry, which is unusual for him,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.53,0:04:18.49,apollon main,Ma,0,0,0,,but I had a hunch he'd be able to eat some watermelon, so I iced one up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.41,0:04:21.49,apollon main,Taichi,0,0,0,,Bro! Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.48,0:04:22.90,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,What's up, Taichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.90,0:04:24.71,apollon main,Taichi,0,0,0,,We found a weird bug!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.71,0:04:25.70,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,A bug?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.70,0:04:26.70,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Is it a big one?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.70,0:04:27.70,apollon main,Taichi,0,0,0,,It's over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.70,0:04:31.19,apollon main,Kota,0,0,0,,Bro, if you plant a watermelon seed, will it grow?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.19,0:04:32.45,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Let's plant one an' see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.45,0:04:33.98,apollon main,Kota,0,0,0,,Look, there!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.21,0:04:34.96,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Oh, there it is!{alt}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.50,0:04:36.98,apollon main,Kota,0,0,0,,It flew!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.98,0:04:39.93,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Yeesh, don't cry about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.46,0:04:43.22,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,A group date?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.22,0:04:47.60,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Yeah. Ri and I will tag along.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.60,0:04:50.34,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,She'll be on guard if you start with just the two of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.34,0:04:53.15,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Yeah, I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.15,0:04:55.73,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Of course, you'll be the one to invite Yurika.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.30,0:04:58.71,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,What's the point if you're \Nnot the one who does it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.71,0:05:01.79,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,I can't! I just don't have it in me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.79,0:05:03.20,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Look...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.76,0:05:05.95,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,What's that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.95,0:05:07.08,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Sarah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.08,0:05:08.23,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Sarah?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.23,0:05:09.41,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,My girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.41,0:05:10.27,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.72,0:05:13.45,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Sarah?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.28,0:05:15.96,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,You're in a bad mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.42,0:05:18.05,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Cute, ain't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.05,0:05:20.10,apollon main,,0,0,0,,Her full name is Sarah Vaughan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.10,0:05:21.56,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,A pigeon, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.79,0:05:24.29,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,What is it, Sarah?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.29,0:05:25.84,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,You're lookin' upset today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.84,0:05:28.03,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,She's probably jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.03,0:05:30.81,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,You've been talking about another girl, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.07,0:05:38.48,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Huh? What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.27,0:05:41.74,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,When did I start enjoying myself?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.32,0:05:46.96,apollon main,Girl,0,0,0,,That was so funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.96,0:05:48.03,apollon main,Yurika,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.43,0:05:52.45,apollon main,Yurika,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.08,0:05:55.20,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.88,0:06:01.48,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I-Idiot! Who goes up to the girl and then runs away?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.48,0:06:02.94,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,I can't do it, man!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.94,0:06:03.85,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Remember the note!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.85,0:06:05.14,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.05,0:06:07.64,apollon main,Girl,0,0,0,,He's coming back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.16,0:06:10.43,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.69,0:06:15.19,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,for suddenly interrupting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.77,0:06:19.33,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Are you free this weekend?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.53,0:06:26.34,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,I would like to take this opportunity to cult... cult...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.34,0:06:27.54,apollon main,Yurika,0,0,0,,"Cultivate."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.54,0:06:30.31,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,cultivate... our friendship!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.58,0:06:30.31,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,That idiot.{alt}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.48,0:06:33.98,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Richie! Richie!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.98,0:06:36.16,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,She said yes! She's goin' with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.94,0:06:40.07,apollon main,Yurika,0,0,0,,We're going to Rendezvous Rock, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.07,0:06:41.93,apollon main,Yurika,0,0,0,,Shall I pack us a lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.74,0:06:46.04,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Um, that'd be great.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.04,0:06:48.67,apollon main,,0,0,0,,Something light like onigiri would be good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.67,0:06:51.12,apollon main,Yurika,0,0,0,,Okay, leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.12,0:06:54.19,apollon main,Yurika,0,0,0,,By the way, just so I know,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.78,0:06:58.69,apollon main,Yurika,0,0,0,,which one of you is inviting me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.68,0:07:00.70,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Oh, that would be...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.58,0:07:05.08,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,This guy! He insisted on inviting you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.08,0:07:06.41,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.43,0:07:08.20,apollon main,Yurika,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.55,0:07:10.09,apollon main,Yurika,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.09,0:07:12.71,apollon main,Yurika,0,0,0,,Well, I'm looking forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.71,0:07:14.34,apollon main,Girl,0,0,0,,You agreed to go on a date?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.34,0:07:15.44,apollon main,Girl,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.21,0:07:18.80,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,You really are a fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.80,0:07:21.92,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,It was going smooth as can be, and then you blew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.92,0:07:25.44,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Yeah, I dunno why I said that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.15,0:07:28.77,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Wind back time for me, Richie!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.77,0:07:29.93,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,As if I can!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.31,0:07:34.69,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Sorry to keep you waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.03,0:07:37.05,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Ah, there's Kaoru!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.48,0:07:41.11,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Hey, what happened to your face?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.11,0:07:43.70,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Just another one of his fights.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.44,0:07:45.95,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Let's go, Kaoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.55,0:07:50.12,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Wait a minute, Ri. One more person will be joining us today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.12,0:07:51.25,apollon main,Yurika,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.25,0:07:52.51,apollon main,Yurika,0,0,0,,I'm late!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.04,0:07:56.41,apollon main,Yurika,0,0,0,,Making lunch took longer than I thought it would.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.86,0:08:02.51,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,You're the girl those hooligans were harassing at the beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.51,0:08:03.18,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Th-That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.67,0:08:06.36,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,You remember her, huh? Actually, today...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.51,0:08:10.03,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Hey! Get a hold of yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.03,0:08:12.62,apollon main,Yurika,0,0,0,,The one with the glasses invited me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.51,0:08:13.48,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,{\an8}Are you all right?! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.48,0:08:14.69,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Kaoru invited you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.69,0:08:16.09,apollon main,Yurika,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.69,0:08:17.48,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,{\an8}What the heck are you doing?! Hey?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.09,0:08:19.66,apollon main,Yurika,0,0,0,,Is it okay for a newcomer like me to intrude?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.12,0:08:19.66,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,{\an8}Get up already!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.66,0:08:23.32,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,O-Oh, of course. The more the merrier!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.71,0:08:23.32,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,{\an8}What's wrong with you today?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.32,0:08:25.10,apollon main,Yurika,0,0,0,,Really? Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.58,0:08:28.74,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Oh, so it was Kaoru that asked her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.07,0:08:37.63,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,She's beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.51,0:08:40.92,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Kaoru must have a weakness for pretty faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.44,0:08:42.76,apollon main,Yurika,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.76,0:08:46.17,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Nothing. I was just thinking that your hat is really stylish.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.17,0:08:47.68,apollon main,Yurika,0,0,0,,Oh, this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.53,0:08:51.13,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Even if I wore it, I'd still look like a yokel.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.13,0:08:53.18,apollon main,Yurika,0,0,0,,Oh, that's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.18,0:08:54.94,apollon main,Yurika,0,0,0,,Pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.73,0:09:03.19,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Ri, when did you change your hairstyle?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.80,0:09:06.76,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Yurika did it for me. What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.76,0:09:09.20,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,It looks super. Really cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.14,0:09:20.21,apollon main,Yurika,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right. I'm told your family owns a record shop, Ritsuko.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.73,0:09:24.21,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Yeah. Do you like jazz, Yurika?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.27,0:09:30.17,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,These two practice playing it together just about every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.17,0:09:31.66,apollon main,Yurika,0,0,0,,They play jazz?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.68,0:09:36.67,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Yup. Kaoru plays piano, and Sentaro plays the drums.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.67,0:09:40.46,apollon main,Yurika,0,0,0,,That's really something! I know \Nsome people who listen to jazz,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.46,0:09:41.98,apollon main,Yurika,0,0,0,,but this is my first time meeting anyone who actually plays it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.42,0:09:45.96,apollon main,Yurika,0,0,0,,My two big brothers like jazz, \Nso I listen too once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.96,0:09:49.82,apollon main,Yurika,0,0,0,,They frown and get a wrinkle between their eyebrows when they listen,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.82,0:09:51.74,apollon main,Yurika,0,0,0,,but I prefer music that really hits you with a bang, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.28,0:09:54.83,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Yeah! That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.83,0:09:57.21,apollon main,Yurika,0,0,0,,I'd love to hear you play the drums.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.21,0:10:03.75,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Y-You can't! I still, uh... stink at it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.75,0:10:08.09,apollon main,Yurika,0,0,0,,Oh, but you know you can't improve unless you have an audience, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.09,0:10:09.76,apollon main,Yurika,0,0,0,,Come on, let me hear you play.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.45,0:10:13.41,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,This... is an unexpected development.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.41,0:10:14.39,apollon main,Yurika,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.76,0:10:17.79,apollon main,Yurika,0,0,0,,Oh, no! I think I got scratched by a branch.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.15,0:10:26.43,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Well, what do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.43,0:10:28.18,apollon main,,0,0,0,,Looks like he's got some moves after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.24,0:10:36.91,apollon main,Yurika,0,0,0,,Hey, I heard a rumor that couples who climb to the top of that rock together will get married.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.18,0:10:40.17,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,No girl's gonna get up that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.17,0:10:42.08,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Richie, you up for it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.08,0:10:43.29,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Why me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.57,0:10:46.27,apollon main,Yurika,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm not letting you get away with saying that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.27,0:10:48.26,apollon main,Yurika,0,0,0,,I can make it that high.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.02,0:10:50.80,apollon main,Yurika,0,0,0,,Would anyone like to go with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.76,0:10:53.39,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Go on!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.69,0:10:55.22,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,N-No!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.24,0:11:03.15,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,I mean, the sign says it's off limits... and it's dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.52,0:11:07.97,apollon main,Yurika,0,0,0,,Oh, that's too bad. I really wanted \Nto see the view from up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.48,0:11:17.10,apollon main,Yurika,0,0,0,,You shouldn't have wolfed it down!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.39,0:11:22.55,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Those two seem to be getting on well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.58,0:11:27.07,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Kaoru, you can have this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.87,0:11:29.17,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.57,0:11:31.26,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,I'm just going to pick some flowers!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.48,0:11:34.56,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Probably the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.98,0:11:40.23,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Boy, this onigiri is huge.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.38,0:12:03.79,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,It's my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.10,0:12:07.21,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I hurt her...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.98,0:12:10.16,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,in the cruelest of ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.15,0:12:15.22,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I made the girl who's most important to me cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.54,0:12:19.22,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Those shoulders look so sad, but I have no right...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.40,0:12:21.76,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,to try and comfort her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.40,0:12:34.99,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Good morning, Kaoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.35,0:12:37.35,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.35,0:12:38.06,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Richie!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.99,0:12:40.85,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,C-Come with me a sec!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.75,0:12:44.75,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Look! This handkerchief!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.15,0:12:48.75,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Yurika gave it to me as an apology for my towel yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.76,0:12:52.38,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,It smells kind of nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.97,0:12:54.63,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Or is it my imagination?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.16,0:13:01.14,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,What the hell was that for?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.97,0:13:07.12,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Kaoru?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.69,0:13:10.11,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I couldn't let you pick up this handkerchief!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.11,0:13:11.99,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I couldn't bear seeing that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.68,0:13:21.41,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,If you're here for the handkerchief, you can have it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.88,0:13:23.77,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I was in the wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.77,0:13:25.60,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,It's all my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.60,0:13:28.08,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,What're you talkin' about? Tell me already!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.08,0:13:29.28,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.28,0:13:32.18,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,You're satisfied as long as you have this handkerchief, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.18,0:13:34.97,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Go home and sniff it all you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.83,0:13:36.93,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.54,0:13:38.93,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,You lookin' to start a fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.35,0:13:43.31,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.31,0:13:46.48,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Sentaro, let go of Kaoru!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.53,0:13:50.48,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,This is stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.82,0:13:52.20,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Don't get rough with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.20,0:13:53.85,apollon main,,0,0,0,,You owe him an apology!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.07,0:13:57.49,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,I don't owe that guy nothin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.89,0:13:59.23,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Wait, Sentaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.13,0:14:03.50,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,You can't forget this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.77,0:14:07.33,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,This handkerchief is important to you, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.15,0:14:14.91,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Kaoru,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.62,0:14:19.80,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,I bet Sentaro is drumming away \Nlike a madman right about now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.58,0:14:22.56,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Richie, you stupid idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.56,0:14:23.13,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.54,0:14:27.21,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,The sooner you make up, the easier it'll be.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.80,0:14:29.17,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Come with me to practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.17,0:14:30.27,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.27,0:14:35.64,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Before you moved here, Sentaro always practiced alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.51,0:14:39.07,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Shutting himself in the basement, \Nnot letting anyone near him...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.12,0:14:42.90,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Even I didn't feel welcome in the basement.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.38,0:14:48.04,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,But ever since you came, that feeling's been gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.04,0:14:51.90,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,I'm positive he's happy that he\N found a friend to play jazz with.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.64,0:14:57.84,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Kaoru, shall I guess what you \Ntwo were fighting about today?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.39,0:15:01.97,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,You like Yurika, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.35,0:15:06.92,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,I bet you got mad at Sentaro for showing off that handkerchief.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.57,0:15:09.96,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,She is really pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.74,0:15:14.11,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,I wish I'd been born looking like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.11,0:15:17.35,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Wh-What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.35,0:15:19.10,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Ri, you're plenty...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.46,0:15:21.55,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,a-attractive.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.40,0:15:28.36,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Thanks for trying to cheer me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.88,0:15:31.67,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I'm not... I wasn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.67,0:15:34.61,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I wasn't trying to cheer you up. I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.80,0:15:38.17,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Here we are!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.76,0:15:40.17,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Well, good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.28,0:15:43.46,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Hey, Ri! Open up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.31,0:15:46.82,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,{\a6}Let me out, Ri!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.78,0:15:46.82,apollon main,Dad,0,0,0,,What's the ruckus, Ritsuko?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.85,0:15:49.21,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Drastic measures.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.97,0:15:54.90,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I-I didn't come here to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.75,0:16:02.69,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.54,0:16:05.69,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,N-Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.92,0:16:13.40,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,He feels the same way about the girl he likes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.12,0:16:27.52,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Hey, don't just join in!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.52,0:16:28.13,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.11,0:16:30.55,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,I wasn't tryin' to join in.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.75,0:16:41.43,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,He's following along again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.80,0:16:55.20,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,What the heck is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.20,0:16:56.29,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Jazz with a festival dance beat!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.29,0:16:59.16,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Cut it out! I can't play if I'm laughing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.84,0:17:36.28,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Next time, maybe I'll play \Nsomething just for Ri.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.97,0:17:42.43,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,And then... maybe I'll try letting her know how I feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.85,0:17:49.09,apollon main,Yurika,0,0,0,,Sentaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.68,0:17:51.05,apollon main,Yurika,0,0,0,,I'm coming in.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.85,0:17:56.31,apollon main,Yurika,0,0,0,,Oh, don't be so stiff.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.52,0:18:04.36,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.62,0:18:07.10,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,hell is he doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.78,0:18:14.74,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I'm sure Ri is thinking about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.83,0:18:20.67,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,310)}Meanwhile, he's...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.92,0:18:25.21,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Um, Ri...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.70,0:18:29.72,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,There's a song that I'd like to play for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.00,0:18:35.30,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I've been practicing my heart out on this song.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.18,0:18:40.97,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I wish I still had more time to work on it,\Nbut I feel like I have to play this for her now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.54,0:18:45.22,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Play through me, Bill Evans.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.83,0:20:11.42,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,"Someday My Prince Will Come."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.17,0:20:14.35,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,That's the title of the song.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.45,0:20:19.36,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,So you're the prince?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.70,0:20:21.01,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,I'm right, aren't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.01,0:20:24.36,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,You've been practicing for Yurika, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.84,0:20:27.18,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,And this is your "dress rehearsal"!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.07,0:20:29.05,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.21,0:20:35.90,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,This is the real performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.64,0:20:40.67,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,You're the one that I like.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.42,0:20:45.90,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,You don't have to give me an answer right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.48,0:20:50.93,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I just wanted to let you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.38,0:20:53.87,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,that there's somebody here who's in love with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.07,0:21:01.40,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Ri's eyes are on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.39,0:21:05.56,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,She's always thinking of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.81,0:21:08.71,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,That doesn't bother me though.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.83,0:21:14.99,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,You taught me that it was possible to fall in love like this.
